                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d51">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Gresham</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Thompson</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1893-10-11">
                            <hi rend="italic">October 11, 1893</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Mr. Gresham instructs Mr. Thompson to exert himself in favor of the innocent
                    trade of American vessels and of the legitimate inward and outward trade of
                    merchandise belonging to the citizens of the United States.</p>
            </div>
